# Directions to L50 Thief GM (Bolehcim, mob 14334)

say { "hello";
	say Hello %n, what can I do for you?;
	}
        
say { "next guildmaster";
	whisper %n Finding your next guildmaster is part of your training.;
	whisper %n All I can tell you is this...;
	whisper %n <p>Bolehcim<1> the hobbit is the new Grandmaster of Thieves.;
	whisper %n He has a secret lair, where exactly no one can say.;
	whisper %n Although my guess is he's in the Shire somewhere.;
	}

say { "Bolehcim";
	whisper %n The key to finding Bolehcim.....;
	whisper %n ...is to know who to bet on.;
	}

